        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Abuse of alcohol or illicit drugs

          -  History of mental retardation or any mental disease

          -  Skin irritation / Atopic dermatitis or any other skin condition at the area of
             patients palms that might affect his/her ability to hold the device appropriately
